{"tid":946454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"整容成癮致毀容 南韓前模特兒離世終年57歲","createTime":"2018-12-18T14:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T04:24:36.000Z","uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28362d92bdc62d83009f0a6bcecee18f7a430eb9","tid":946454,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181218&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59043052\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181218%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59043052&d=qAjeUnq431rM%2BBBwyK7Hkf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=2e940b42\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20181218%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D59043052&h=99219966\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20181218&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=59043052</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓前模特兒韓慧景本來外貌娟好，年輕時赴日本發展，卻因不滿自己外觀接受非法整容手術後，臉部腫成3倍大而毀容，慘被稱為「風扇阿姨」。南韓傳媒更傳出她已於本月15日過世，終年57歲，結束其悲慘一生。<br />\n<br />\n韓慧景年輕時夢想成為歌手，愛美的她整容整上癮，在臉上不斷注射矽膠，結果令臉部腫脹，最後醫生說她心理有問題，拒絕再為她動手術。不過她未有停手，反而自己買矽膠和食油注射，最終毀容。由於面部腫大，她面容盡毀後曾表示無法閉上眼睛睡覺，說話時會漏風，不時遭路人嘲笑，被稱為「風扇阿姨」。<br />\n<br />\n2004年她曾上電視節目訴說自己的情況，引來外界關注，並得到觀眾捐款資助接受重整手術。經過17次手術後，她的臉部腫脹情況有改善，但頭部卻留下巨大的異物，令她視力衰弱，到2012年，日本知名整容醫生高須克彌自願替她進行手術，取出240克的異物後，她的腫脹狀況緩和，但外表始終駭人。<br />\n<br />\n韓慧景2015年最後一次在觀眾前露臉，但她一直持續接受捐款進行手術，卻在上周六突然離世，葬禮也低調舉行。她的家人並未透露她的死因，僅表示她周日已出殯，令大批南韓及日本民眾十分震驚，「風扇阿姨」也一度登上南韓入門網站NAVER的搜索關鍵字第一名。"},{"pid":"2d8f868fc94653a101e9cb2f6dab80b8b056cd97","tid":946454,"uid":51720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成癮嘅極致 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74f9448416077353952195fb86be37f9e8290f4f","tid":946454,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:07:24.000Z","msg":"弱柒智<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427d39ea8684e72257e72760ac69e9c226359acd","tid":946454,"uid":81518,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"319a155867c8602e2ecc50a6ad3d833c3dec341f","tid":946454,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"427d39ea8684e72257e72760ac69e9c226359acd","tid":946454,"uid":81518,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:07:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:10:19.000Z","msg":"既然咁想要圖，而家畀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R2H5Cc1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR2H5Cc1.png&h=bf359fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71yXtjH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71yXtjH.png&h=8bde169c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ea7b813d45ee1b649d19c4b3dde292d48d2e9252","tid":946454,"uid":148189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-18T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"等睇幾時到大馬既代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda260353a83a09522b058fdb56affc77eff2c84","tid":946454,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手術成功"},{"pid":"400eba49f1ea9bc03d225150515b55d3bc846b66","tid":946454,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:23:54.000Z","msg":"香港都見到好多整容西，個樣好撚怪"},{"pid":"2de7cb580fe8ee39ff635c13708c9dadea38df09","tid":946454,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T04:24:36.000Z","msg":"面目全非腳"}]}